# Alembic Commands — A-01 Cheatsheet

## Setup
```bash
alembic current          # Show current revision
alembic history --verbose  # Show all revisions
```

## Migration
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "create ledger_entries table"
alembic upgrade head     # Apply all
alembic upgrade +1       # Apply one step
alembic downgrade -1     # Roll back one step
alembic downgrade base   # Roll back all
```

## Debug
```bash
alembic show <rev_id>    # Show details of a revision
alembic heads            # Show branch heads
```
